{{Youmay|the wind spirit known as Grael|the [[Ewok/Legends|Ewok]] warrior of the [[Grael|same name]]}}
'''Grael''' was a notable deity in [[Ewok/Legends|Ewok]] legends, which told of a wind spirit that carried the scent of smoke to Ewoks, warning them of forest fires on the [[Endor/Legends|Endor moon]]. "Grael" was a common name for Ewok males, taken from their mythology as many of that species' names were,<ref name="GCG">''[[Galactic Campaign Guide]]''</ref> such as [[Grael|the warrior]] from the [[Panshee]] tribe.<ref name="SWAJ 1">{{JournalCite|1|Escape from Balis-Baurgh}}</ref>

